    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You curse the target, sapping its spirit and leaving a contagious trap in its essence. The target must attempt a Will save. Any creature that casts a divine or occult spell on the target while it's affected is targeted by spiritual epidemic and must also attempt a Will save. The curse continues to spread in this way.</p>\r<p>\n<hr><b>Critical Success</b>  The target is unaffected.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Success</b>  The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled} 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied} 2 for 1 round.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Failure</b>  The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled} 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied} 2 for 1 minute and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled} 1 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied} 1 permanently.</p>\r<p>\n<b>Critical Failure</b>  The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled} 3 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied} 3 for 1 minute and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.MIRkyAjyBeXivMa7]{Enfeebled} 2 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionspf2e.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied} 2 permanently.</p>",
